INFRASTRUCTURE AFTER

START-UP.

THE MAXIMUM TOTAL PRODUCTION FROM TOMBUA AND LANDANA OF

100,000 BARRELS OF CRUDE OIL PER DAY IS EXPECTED TO OCCUR

