CHEVRON PARTICIPATED IN THREE SUCCESSFUL DEEPWATER EXPLORATION

WELLS DURING 2008. HYDROCARBONS WERE CONFIRMED IN TWO WELLS IN

OPL 214 AND ONE WELL IN OML 113. ADDITIONAL RESERVOIR STUDIES

