DURING 2008, THE COMPANY COMPLETED THE CONSTRUCTION OF A NATURAL

GAS GATHERING PIPELINE SERVING THE PICEANCE BASIN IN NORTHWEST

COLORADO; PARTICIPATED IN THE SUCCESSFUL INSTALLATION OF THE

