INCOME IN 2007 OF $10.3 BILLION INCREASED $1.4 BILLION FROM 2006. EARNINGS IN 2007 BENEFITED

APPROXIMATELY $1.6 BILLION FROM HIGHER PRICES, PRIMARILY FOR CRUDE OIL, AND $300 MILLION FROM

