FOR SEVERAL YEARS BECAUSE OF THE COMPLEXITY, SCALE

AND NEGOTIATIONS CONNECTED WITH THE PROJECTS. THE

MAJORITY OF THESE DECISIONS ARE EXPECTED TO OCCUR IN

THE NEXT THREE YEARS.

