NOTE

22

EMPLOYEE BENEFIT PLANS - CONTINUED

SHARES HELD IN THE LESOP ARE RELEASED AND

ALLOCATED TO THE ACCOUNTS OF PLAN PARTICIPANTS BASED

ON DEBT SERVICE DEEMED TO BE PAID IN THE YEAR IN

