INCLUDES YEAR-END RESERVE QUANTITIES RELATED TO PRODUCTION-SHARING CONTRACTS (PSC)

(REFER TO PAGE E-146 FOR THE DEFINITION OF A PSC). PSC-RELATED RESERVE QUANTITIES ARE 40 PERCENT, 37

